arts.ttl: Swansea City 3-2 Nottingham Forest: Burgess bags brace to boot Forest out at the death
arts.sum: Substitute Zan Vipotnik's flicked effort levelled the tie, and centre-back Burgess matched the feat of Jesus with a brace to send the Swansea faithful into raptures. Igor Jesus scored an impressive brace for the visitors before Cameron Burgess' header pegged them back.
